@2571  for some conversation.

If the question is about calcentral forms, I honestly have no idea and if you had a conflict approved and were put on the waitlist the conflict would still exist and would keep you from being enrolled through automatic waitlist processing.  CS conflict forms are processed every three days and I believe EE conflict forms even more often.

children.subject: I think you are referring to the SIS conflict form as I see you filled out the department's EE conflict form today for the first time. There's one person ahead of you for EE126. I check this form about every other day.
